# Project Context

- Objective: Jin Yong style Chinese wuxia generation.
- Base model: `Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct`.
- Runtime target: Kaggle T4 16GB with QLoRA.
- Dataset schema: `instruction`, `input`, `output` in UTF-8 JSONL.
